transforms.result: :root{color-scheme:only light;--black-body:#161313;--black:#151515;--white:#fff;--grey-hr:hsla(0,0%,99%,.5);--grey-span:hsla(0,0%,99%,.7);--dark-grey:#333;--grey-blue:#2f314d;--dark-blue:#3c3f63;--light-blue:#48abed;--button-pink:#fa2a6f;--jira:#2684ff;--violet:#b724b7;--aws:#f90;--tc-secondary:#8c8c8e;--tc-grey:#cacace;--bg-color:#303030;--bg-secondary-color:#20202a;--empty-color:#191923;--fw-bold:700;--fw-semibold:600;--fw-medium:500;--fw-regular:400;--fs-primary:1rem;--fs-caption:0.8rem;--border-radius:5px;--insent-sm:0.3rem}body,button,input{background-color:var(--black-body);color:var(--white);font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;font-weight:var(--fw-regular)}.overflow-hidden{overflow:hidden}.container-1440{margin:0 auto;max-width:1440px;padding:0 70px}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px){.container-1440{padding:0 32px}}@media only screen and (max-width:768px){.container-1440{padding:0 24px}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px){.container-1440{padding:0 16px}}
